<div id="review_838335845" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/838335845" />
    <a title="June" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/430751-june"><img alt="June" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_50x66-6a03a5c12233c941481992b82eea8d23.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/838335845?book_show_action=true">Jan 29, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="June" class="user" itemprop="url" name="June" href="/user/show/430751-june">June</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Lackey fans and people who enjoy novel retellings of fairy tales</span></div>

          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to June by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/3837733-joan">Joan</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/430751-june?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/430751-june?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/430751-june?shelf=werewolves">werewolves</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/430751-june?shelf=magic">magic</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer838335845" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16747086373668021566">This was a fun quick read. I was a little worried when she wore the red cloak to visit Granny, but Beauty is a spunky, no nonsense character and I enjoyed reading about her. I do think I need breaks from the series and that I enjoy them much more not read back to back.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


